# Allowed declared dependencies for :core.
#
# Adding a new dependency to this module ships it to every consumer of the
# Lemonade design system. New entries require maintainer approval as part of
# the same PR that edits build.gradle.kts.
#
# Format: one entry per line as `<configuration> <expression>`.
# Lines starting with `#` and blank lines are ignored.
#
# (no declared dependencies — all configuration comes from the lemonade convention plugin)
